,Not Recommended,406310,20777760,"Posted: 26 January, 2016",all,MakoSipper,"This is an online version of a famous game with many names, among which: Stop, Adedonha, Stadt Land Fluss, Tutti Frutti, Jeu du Bac, Scattegories...I really like the original pen & paper game, and I'm pretty sure this game can and probably will be nice in the future. But, for now this game has some big issues, so, if you don't have it already, I'd recommend you wait a little bit more before you get it.The devs have been active in the forums, so chances are those will get fixed sooner or later:- Some bugs that make points not be counted- Some weird things, like considering all votes invalid if you just fail to click ""Validate"" in time, even if you had unchecked a few options- Almost no playerbase, despite the 10k copy giveaway on SG- No explanation for people who don't know the game very well- Lacks a lot of interesting functionalities, like:* Chat in the main lobby* Being able to edit themes and other stuff after creating a room* Having more ways to customize the game, like raising Validation timeIf the devs are reading this, don't get demotivated. I'm sure you can make it better and I'll change my review when I think my overall experience is more on the good side. For now, I have to tell I was a bit disappointed."
